 existing placeholder uses a generic coordinate, which seems okay. I need to think through using `sun.misc.Unsafe`, even though it involves reflection, which might not cover everything properly. I could add a helper `UnsafeAllocator`, but it might get flagged, so I'll need to consider if user-code filtering can help mitigate that.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0253e81474ed6bf8016a1e9c58652c8194a6db59fec2516e7b\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqHpyAjDsetL-iP3tjX1gGy6Qrz74HAFVwTIW-JlZN5yCMRSHpsaWoAXSZUZHLfESKHAM_FDYM81kwkOqvSDOOJp585CFUAIEgFYpTKxa54D0SLfcIeXTNL_zlh6sqIlp39GpRKXPz4Q4qrdvcpr8wT-rvw6r0NbIukZ6mvy7nXu9ZwNoq2t5nFiIjEFeEGwEmobWdeUiDpuUfzNZyzBEcHRZlSWXw-R-mE2LSNfP4Y30oHlD3ZjTGIna-73SYzH9ApZSpFQwL-3OKHHbxEzJUuRAILC5mozJownKuAcanEH_dlz37MOVKfD0r-wMfIkXdgjcZq0HDRNhArH19RiyDZqmmljm-D6w92CBCtXCwzgKM8ja5qpQxphxnuCMtYaPLbJQiaY2JMJTDiKk2s8lmgGWYJ-0qPYdl4Ls2fN8vw5yVboXOWE5ReJ4nm8S2Rs2-I2I0EKdnX5Fp4ApqjW1mhz-b3Jf5O7hNQam7Ec8z5lEonWyXxcFNSUFFE05OKP5IQzjjmH7VLytRANiASieiX27ppsh8Yikb7y-1_imoaa49c75_IVzcUrFIIOOI3fOiOQpK8CTwVg3gEwa--sUxv3jiaTgDDQRdGTNRdzyjX7zm4Q5cAyowHp2niOsmsdKuS4CUHOISotJtDj67bO1BBU_VMNQrzphKZ5aN954HBFKL4fh8vFn-aincTt3UEIZcuGikS0Jcc7MmwVLfqMBPtufmWv6sOUpa4PRrFu-Sm1Z5Ix4I8zbYwUdVbv7o4L-_ezBdwEYaGk2umLF4PVR_yBUQsNFhYPrbm_OH9oTDBasL6lcdVEPECfbBujIORKoipA_t5kNJjAGbkPjmNi8M7tmDUzmZiWXiVpYgsrLi9rrkNkM5PFdW6rPTyLNiHiHPT1PBWjH-dyyMSvvyzBRBm3qZZYd0txmw5W6QzXVECHDkM-Huks3uamnOeWPaOzb4_VRB8hdGwvq2aVFgU5Dg90nD8zE3t6Is5XjiqQ22nR_BD1Nz5VfVvtm4oM0Yy0lRr0VNbkAFR1DNm1ujz79gpO0qBB4_sPdrfSKUPrVC5YDi1IRNq3HpvGEf63BX2YOrVgxyVDsgQDJ9mu4LHz5NuKu6ZpUbcyv-lHjMUm8Pjt3QCTkrdXUTLG_wmdZzOB-YyM07US2HzmQta68alHpR6avcrAOb94k5zlgswlYlBVSsOadWy5Tb5eWr2vpcZShHo3Pmvb_uqBopSvQruuvgrX6FwHxm6ZdAMJpx8GzEn-qgdAPGQQTkPeJEqq5Psp_fjoRLKkvgDpNTpXKquehlRqVySYxqWiKzo06DSAdySMtKT9cw67vt8bXyks2tjs3QF8GrwAON6raT5Q9D3eFJj0k_ujsVGYb1VQcWEOxwBRm5hOdpsnkwtLHc-8omMLO8fPJBrhufLBSA_3YX14abJVNKDDZv44knDqxZBy6klnemYbm46ahi6ciQ23k_r09RhTolXrGu-_hdw0GRrJU99fTSNfRrCHG3hyc6qcZJhKP18u8MUm